{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Fund culturally appropriate retirement support for Polish veterans and families",
        "additional_details": "We call on the Government to provide funding to ensure there is culturally appropriate retirement provision for Polish veterans, such as the Ilford Park Polish Home.",
        "background": "We call on the Government to fund the continued operation of culturally appropriate retirement provision to Polish veterans and their families. Such homes provide culturally specific care for elderly residents. The last home of its kind, Ilford Park Polish Home, is due to be closed.",
